decref Inner #1 rc=1 [ownership-edge-cases.main]
decref Wrapper #2 rc=0 [ownership-edge-cases.main]
decref Inner #1 rc=0 [ownership-edge-cases.main]
  free Inner #1
free Wrapper #2 [ownership-edge-cases.main]
```
